<P>
My husband and I would like to voice our appreciation of "Murphy's Law." The 
stories are well-written, the characters have lots of charm, interest and 
believability, and all the actors portraying the leads are terrific. George 
Segal is wonderful, as usual, but the others are truly entertaining. 
</P>
<P>
Mr. and Mrs. R.E. Brock, San Clemente 
