Azusa Pacific, 120-7. In triangular scoring, the Bruins had 96 points, with Cal 
finishing second with 38; CS Northridge was next with 34, and Azusa Pacific 
scored 2 points. 
</P>
<P>
Kevin Williams of UCLA won the men's 100 meters in 10.54 seconds and anchored 
the Bruins' 400-meter relay team, which won in 40.29. 
